{"tid":1598511,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"港產片《獅子山上》《再見UFO》成亞洲電影節開幕電影","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:59:03.000Z","uid":15213,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad476317f582a26695c968de0e14625ba75491b7","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"Source: 官方fb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKAFF/posts/2950982374931474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKAFF%2Fposts%2F2950982374931474&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=45c0010f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKAFF/posts/2950982374931474</a>"},{"pid":"4a89ea97e6b658b6489abf057961efa173ddd2f6","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"今年唔洗估估下，一次過講俾你知開幕電影係邊兩套啦～<br />\n兩部開幕片都是由在電視電影方面有資深背景的導演新作品。<br />\n<br />\n當中有《死開啲啦》導演梁國斌新作《獅子山上》！👨🏻&zwj;🦽<br />\n以「長洲包山王」黎志偉的真人真事改編的勵志故事，由林德信、衛詩雅、朱鑑然及袁澧林主演。講述國際級攀石運動員黎志偉因車禍意外而半身不遂後，他如何再次奮鬥起來🔥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdP4PPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdP4PPS.jpg&h=14f4aaeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b17dfc104e0a2d584cc0c897c2170a12644eb22","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"另一部是梁栢堅執導，充滿昔日香港情懷的《再見UFO》🛸<br />\n三位主角蔡卓妍、徐天佑及黃又南繼電影《這個夏天有異性》，17年後再度合作。故事發生在80年代中，香港華富邨出現UFO的都市傳說，三位主角飾演在屋邨長大的少年共同見證當年UFO飛過的事蹟以及之後的成長故事🏘️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/geQfWvc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgeQfWvc.jpg&h=36d83252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b8a12da253e7878ce28afce039f67660eebbf9f","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:22:06.000Z","msg":"兩套都係Golden Scene出<br />\n一套真人真事勵志<br />\n一套奇情加（相信係）Shine最後一次一齊拍戲<br />\n<br />\n大家期唔期待？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a010331e391c89301ae185923810b06988a83d91","tid":1598511,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"c0712b9b9bb27a5de9d4ed619c84a43715e9f6f1","tid":1598511,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"再見UFO係咪大陸唔上?"},{"pid":"22790c617d6522583e55e0d62c3be3a244fa3388","tid":1598511,"uid":106785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"有天佑但有蝗又藍 睇唔睇好"},{"pid":"2f6c07ab871538d647f8faf36411b37a7c5971ba","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22790c617d6522583e55e0d62c3be3a244fa3388","tid":1598511,"uid":106785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"有天佑但有蝗又藍 睇唔睇好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"世紀難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8ec5077b58889944ba096725f161d743b3f559","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0712b9b9bb27a5de9d4ed619c84a43715e9f6f1","tid":1598511,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"再見UFO係咪大陸唔上?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔多覺有消息<br />\n而家合作片通常仲會早過香港上<br />\n同埋UFO大陸都唔慌批啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95935445cb94fa0b6446a2ea0cefa140bcba054b","tid":1598511,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6c07ab871538d647f8faf36411b37a7c5971ba","tid":1598511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22790c617d6522583e55e0d62c3b